rows.label: qst710204_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, it's you. I've been waiting.
Did you catch any fish?

rows.label: qst710204_msg0102
rows.name:
I can't believe you actually managed
to collect this many fish...

rows.label: qst710204_msg0103
rows.name:
Alright, wait a moment... With
this, that moat will be revived.

rows.label: qst710204_msg0201
rows.name:
A moat of that size... still
needs more fish. Please!

rows.label: qst710204_msg0202
rows.name:
A large fish with ferocious fangs would
be good. It would be especially popular
with the brave people of Iira.
